    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Pronotal surface of females in dorsal view. A, Bothynus entellus; B, B. stenelus; C, B. tricornis; D, B. araya. Proventrite of females in ventral view. E, Bothynus entellus (small furrows, arrow); F, B. araya (long furrow, arrow). Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3702889/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3702891>
